title: Windows 10 Pro-Core X86 MULTi-14 Dec 2015 {Generation2}
description:
* Windows 10 Pro-Core X86 MULTi-14 Dec 2015 {Generation2} 


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one SOURCE ISO and thirteen 
* executable SFV-files.

* All SFV-files are created from WINDOWS 10 TH2 BUILD 10586
* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the 
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source) 
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference. 

* Files: 
* Win10.X86.en-US.ISO 
* Size: 2,96GB

[ SVF-FILES ] 

* Win10.X86.da-DK - 186MB
* Win10.X86.de-DE - 303MB
* Win10.X86.en-GB - 282MB
* Win10.X86.es-ES - 290MB
* Win10.X86.fi-FI - 187MB
* Win10.X86.fr-FR - 289MB
* Win10.X86.it-IT - 251MB
* Win10.X86.nb-NO - 197MB
* Win10.X86.nl-NL - 204MB
* Win10.X86.pl-PL - 217MB
* Win10.X86.pt-BR - 234MB
* Win10.X86.pt-PT - 179MB
* Win10.X86.sv-SE - 182MB

* Hashes attached in a separate .txt

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ] 

* Windows 10 Home - - - STD
* Windows 10 Home - - - KMS
* Windows 10 Pro- - - - STD
* Windows 10 Pro- - - - KMS

* STD = Standard installation
* KMS = Pre-Activated

* Activator: KMSpico 10.1.9 
( Potential False Positive Virus Alarm )

[url]http://postimg.org/gallery/3ap1hkrl8/[/url]

[ CONTENTS ]

* Integrated / Pre-installed in Audit Mode:

* KB3103688
* KB3116278
* KB3116908

* SetupComplete / Post-install:

* .NET Framework 3.5
* Defender Updates
 
[ FEATURES ]

* UEFI-ready 
* (Use attached Rufus USB-tool to make UEFI-bootable).
* Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset 10.0 (Microsoft DaRT) 

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ] 

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language.exe
* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO
 
* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ISO in the selected language. 

[ INSTALLATION & INFORMATION ]

* Create bootable USB (highly recommended) with Rufus,
* (attached) or burn to DVD at slow speed.
